Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards

Record Class CardSlot

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards.CardSlot
Record Components:
card - a reference to the Card object contained by the slot
onBackSide - true if the card is on the back side, false otherwise
placementTurn - a number representing the placement turn during which the card was placed (if it was ever placed)
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public record CardSlot(Card card, boolean onBackSide, int placementTurn) extends Record implements Serializable
Record that represent a Card along with its orientation and placement turn number (if the card was placed) It also "remap" certain Card methods in order to take advantage of the information in the record.
